aima.core.logic.propositional.kb.data

Class ConjunctionOfClauses

  • java.lang.Object
    • aima.core.logic.propositional.kb.data.ConjunctionOfClauses

  • public class ConjunctionOfClauses
extends java.lang.Object
    Artificial Intelligence A Modern Approach (3rd Edition): page 253.

    A conjunction of clauses, where each clause is a disjunction of literals. Here we represent a conjunction of clauses as a set of clauses, where each clause is a set of literals. In addition, a conjunction of clauses, as implemented, are immutable.
    Author:
    Ciaran O'Reilly
